  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"page phb\" id=\"p37\"><div class=\"columnWrapper\"><p>You generate an orb of soothing wind and press it against your body, causing an aura of healing wind to surround you. If you possess the bleeding and/or chilled conditions, they are immediately removed.</p><p>For the duration, you recover 1d4+1 hit points at the start of each of your turns, and have advantage on saving throws to resist the bleeding and chilled conditions.</p></div></div><div class=\"page phb\" id=\"p38\"><div class=\"columnWrapper\"><p>Additionally, effects that would give you either listed condition without a saving throw, instead enable you to make a Constitution saving throw, resisting gaining the condition(s) on a success.</p></div></div>",
